.TH GKN 1 "2026-02-03" "gkn" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gkn \- safety-first local GitHub repo management CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gkn
.RI [ --json ]
.RI <command>
.RI [ args... ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B gkn
runs local-only, non-interactive GitHub repo management commands with a deny-first safety guard.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B repo
Repo operations.
.TP
.B skills
Skills sync operations.
.TP
.B config
Config operations.
.TP
.B doctor
Environment checks.
.TP
.B version
Show version.
.TP
.B clone
Clone a repo (shortcut).
.TP
.B quickstart
Create a new repo (shortcut).
.SH COMMON FLAGS
.TP
.B --json
Machine-readable output.
.TP
.B --only
Repeatable glob filter (repo/skills commands).
.TP
.B --exclude
Repeatable glob filter (repo/skills commands).
.TP
.B --dry-run
Do not write changes.
.TP
.B --force
Allow destructive actions.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/github-kanri/config.json
Config file.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 1
Error.
.SH SEE ALSO
README.md, docs/usage.md, docs/config.md
